==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crudeness
<hw>Crude"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A crude, undigested, or
unprepared state; rawness; unripeness; immatureness; unfitness for a
destined use or purpose; <as>as, the <ex>crudeness</ex> of iron ore;
<ex>crudeness</ex> of theories or plans</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>crudites</ent>⟦br⟧
